&lt;div class="hextra-success-icon hx:hidden hx:group-[.copied]/copybtn:block hx:pointer-events-none hx:h-4 hx:w-4">&lt;/div>
&lt;/button>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;h2>Watch for&lt;span class="hx:absolute hx:-mt-20" id="watch-for">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#watch-for" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Rails cookie/session migrations&lt;/strong> where old serializers are
still enabled.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Background job payload formats&lt;/strong> shared across deploy waves.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>&lt;code>aliases: true&lt;/code>&lt;/strong> in YAML parsers reopening gadget vectors.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;strong>Monkey patches in initializers&lt;/strong> that re-enable unsafe
loading globally.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
